chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
Hey there
awesome! we're at the starting point, we see a twig to the left leading to a small island with a tiger on it
what is our first move?
Head towards the tiger but between the stick and the rock on the island
alright, keeping a safe distance from that tiger
we're now at the island with the butterfly and the parrot. it's a bit confusing, what should we do next?
you should be on the island with the tiger, between the rock and the stick facing the butterfly
my bad, i got confused. thanks
now we're on the tiger's island, facing the butterfly. what's next?
ok now go over the other stick towads the parrot and go around the parrot on the left side and in between the elephant and cross the river on the rocks
got it, going around the parrot left side and heading to the elephant crossing the river on the rocks
we're now at a new island with a frog, and a crocodile to the left of the frog. where to now?
start going under the frog and go a little further then do a u turn and hug the tree until you cross over the crocidile and onto the large black rock
okie dokie, heading under the frog, making a u-turn, and crossing over by hugging the tree to reach the crocodile
now go from that large black rock to the rock bridge that heads to the left twards the girrafe
gotcha! heading left over the rock bridge towards the giraffe
go under the girrafe and crose the the next island, go through the snake and your at the treasure in the open space to the right of the tree
alright, going under the giraffe, crossing to the next island, then through the snake to the treasure
and we're there! *finished* you're one heck of an instructor! can't wait for the next map
hola, q tal? ready to go?
Hey im ready
awesome! take few steps to your left, towards the wooden bench, got it?
yup
cool! cross that trail now and just when you're nearly at the florist stand, surprise! whip a 180 degree turn to your left and head back towards our fluffy friend
got it
yoohoo! now cross over the branch and keep heads up to the south
peek the picnic? you should see another white dog chilling there
yeah
fantastic! keep your course and slightly veer to the west, over the picnic mat
be careful not to step on the berries!
ok and the berries are safe
haha, those berries thank you! now, head towards the wooden branch and cross that river to the north
got ya
great job! now, do see that green bush? give it a little space, circle it from the right, and head over to the florist stand
k in front of the stand
awesome- sauce! now, do a smooth left and keep going till you see a big bridge with cyclists on it
pass that bridge to the west side
ok crossing now
just past the bridge, take a moment to rest, and look at the elderly folks enjoying their newspapers on the bench
lovely, isn't it?
sure is ha
alright, shake a leg south now, between the old folks and the wooden branch
soon you'll reach a green bush near the end of the branch
right infront of the bush
nice one! now sneak your way east, between the branch and the bush, will ya?
hola, q tal? ready to start?
Alright ready
super :) i'm at the tent in the north
where to next, mate?
lets head south between the rock wall and bush with the dog and do a slight curve on the top edge of the path between the dog and gril and over teh campe fire
cool! now i'm between the rock wall and the dog, making a slight curve around the top of the path
i am heading towards the campfire. what's next?
go above and around the camp fire towards the path an dunder the mushroom, get to just in front of the blue car and make a a u turn back to where the path forks
got it! i'm circling the campfire, passing under the mushroom and stopping in front of the blue car
now, i'm making a u-turn back to where the path forks. what's the next move?
now head south down the path, when you get to the telescope cut between it and the push to the path below
roger that! just cut between the telescope and the bush, now on the path below
where to now?
then go left on the path and cut through wher ethe rock wall mets the circular rock wall to the cabin
okay, left on the path it is
now, i'm cutting through where the rock wall meets the circular one. hello cabin! *finished*
hey there, estas listo?
Si
awesome! let's get this started, dude. first up, go under that first palm tree
veer right and pass the second one. now, take a hard left before the third tree and head south. let me know when you're there
i think so
cool! now, see that brown puppy? move to its left, hang a slight left, and then turn right to the south
you with me?
i thought i was already by the third tree past the puppie
right on! now what i need next is for you to squeeze between that big rock on your left and the small rock on your right
head straight until you touch the water. can you see it?
got it
sweet! take a dip and you'll see a big red crab. don't be scared of mr
crabby! just turn right and swim along the big rock, heading westwards. tell me once there
in front of the crab by the big rock
fantastic! now, keep going west until you see a medium rock
when a shark looms in the water, don't freak out - just turn sharp right!
ok
great! time to head back to dry land, my friend
navigate between that medium rock and the funky colored ball. head north, okay?
got it
lovely! next, make a soft left and go northwest
you'll see a red tent to your left and a big speaker to your right
ok and then
then, sneak around the tent, kinda like doing a mini lap around it
keep going south till you see the sea
ok
perfect! now, just when you're about to hit those waves, i want you to turn right and go below that red kayak
you see it?
yes
awesome! now take a sharp turn to the right, keep going along the kayak till you spot a small green bush
go ahead buddy
k
awesome job, mate! you've reached the final spot! how's the view from there?
